**Calculation of the transport cost thanks to the Transport Costs app: benefits for the user**

úÿÿÿÿÿÿÿÿ **Calculation of the shipping cost on the Sales Oder card.**

Provides the ability to select shipping agent / shipping service depending on the summary of transport costs compatible with the active price lists

úÿÿÿÿÿÿÿÿ **Transport** **costs per document**

ÿSummary calculation for single document or period (e.g. at the end of the month all transport costs incurred for shipments are recalculated)

úÿÿÿÿÿÿÿÿ **Manual modification of the shipping cost**

Possibility to modify the "estimate" transport costs calculated on the basis of additional services agreed with the carrier

úÿÿÿÿÿÿÿÿ **From estimate to final balance**

ÿOnce all the transport costs relating to a shipping agent have been defined and controlled, the costs are made definitive (e.g. check the purchase invoice of the vendor / shipper) ÿ